---
layout: base-it.njk
title: Blog
description: Tutti gli articoli su It's A Malamute — razza, addestramento, salute, alimentazione, attrezzatura e aggiornamenti.
permalink: /it/blog/
---

<section class="cat-hero">
  <div class="container cat-hero-inner">
    <p class="cat-hero-eyebrow">It's A Malamute</p>
    <h1 class="cat-hero-title">Tutti gli articoli</h1>
    <p class="cat-hero-desc">Guide pratiche, esperienze dirette e aggiornamenti su tutto ciò che riguarda l'Alaskan Malamute.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container breadcrumb-inner">
    <a href="/it/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
    <span>Blog</span>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="cat-posts-section">
  <div class="container">
    {% set allPosts = collections.it_posts | reverse %}
    {% if allPosts and allPosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="posts-grid">
      {% for post in allPosts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
        <div class="post-card-image">
          {% if post.data.cover %}
            <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
          {% else %}
            <div class="post-card-placeholder">🐾</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="post-card-body">
          <div class="post-card-cat">{{ post.data.category or "Articolo" }}</div>
          <h2 class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}
          <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="post-card-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div style="text-align:center; padding: 80px 0; color: var(--text-light);">
      <p style="font-family: var(--ff-mono); font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;">Prossimamente</p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--arctic);">I primi articoli sono in arrivo.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
